<p>A simple web app where a user can:</p>
<ul>
  <li>Create an account (Devise)</li>
  <li>Perform the all CRUD operations on his recipes, while getting nutritional information about each ingredient and recipe created</li>
  <li>Save to favourites</li>
  <li>Choose to publish or not his recipes</li>
  <li>Search recipes by recipe name or ingredient (ElasticSearch with Searchkick and Bonsai gems)</li>
</ul>
